Example C
Is 20, 21, 29 a Pythagorean triple?
If 202 +212 = 292, then the set is a Pythagorean triple.
202 +212 = 400+441 = 841
292 = 841
Therefore, 20, 21, and 29 is a Pythagorean triple.
